title: Studio Apt in Loring Park
posting_body: ['Opening at Loring Manor Apartments.', ' Classic brownstone in a great downtown location!', '  We have a studio/efficiency', 'apartment for September 1, 2022.', '  Rent is $775.00.', '    The heat, garbage, water, sewer, and gas are included.', '  The tenants pay their own electricity and television/cable.', 'Conveniently located in the Loring Park are, Loring Manor provides affordable downtown living.', ' Centered in the Minneapolis cultural hub, the Walker Art Center, the Art Institute and Orchestra Hall area are less then 5 minutes away.', '  Close to bus lines, MCTC, and St Thomas Law School.', 'Lease: One year', 'Deposit: $775.00', 'Parking:  Off street parking lot behind building, assigned spaces $90.00/month', 'Application fee:  $45 nonrefundable', 'Please call Aram at', 'show contact info', 'or the Main office at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing.']
